==English==

===Etymology===
[[counter-]] + [[sign]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# a second [[signature]] added to a document to affirm the [[validity]] of the signature of the first [[person]]

===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb}}

# to add a second [[signature]] to a document, affirming the [[validity]] of the signature of another [[person]]

